{"tid":2415293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街場重開爆滿 安心碼冇人理","createTime":"2021-02-20T06:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T07:15:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6949bcdb9f5865bfb50aeb4462cd4b33948350","tid":2415293,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:50:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/6N4UZVA7A5EGLFMHQMKMPZDEXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2F6N4UZVA7A5EGLFMHQMKMPZDEXU%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=7448db9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2F6N4UZVA7A5EGLFMHQMKMPZDEXU%2F&h=b56a62e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/6N4UZVA7A5EGLFMHQMKMPZDEXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n街場重開爆滿 安心碼冇人理<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎第四波去年底爆發，體育場所12月初關閉，直至近日疫情放緩，大部份康文署轄下體育館及戶外硬地球場昨日終解封，雖然街場外貼着「安心出行」二維碼，但有巿民指街場「冇人理」，二維碼作用不大。另外，修頓及麥花臣等多個街場仍用作流動檢測站，「餓波」甚久的巿民應留意資訊避免摸門釘。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：孕婦 重病者 不宜接種科興  專家：長者數據太少 想知答案強人所難<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n修頓及麥花臣仍為檢測站<br />\n<br />\n球迷苦等兩個多月，終等到球場昨日重開，維園四個籃球場全部爆滿，足球場亦有十多人「鬥波」。康文署曾發聲明表示，使用者進入體育處所、表演場地、博物館和公共圖書館前必須利用手機掃描安心出行二維碼，或登記姓名、電話及到訪日期時間，以便出現確診個案時作追蹤；惟球場邊鐵絲網及球柱雖貼着多張安心出行二維碼，但驟眼看沒人掃碼。<br />\n<br />\n就讀中四的Katie跟兩位朋友到維園打籃球，她認為二維碼作用不大：「咁大個球場，冇保安睇住，都唔會理咁多。」她續指希望到體育館打球，惟在康體通預訂系統可見多個球場已租出，故會繼續到街場。留學英國的Jasper昨晨獨自到維園打球，他透露去年12月底返港時已封場，十分「餓波」，未來會相約好友一起到街場打球。<br />\n<br />\n康文署轄下部份體育場所依然關閉，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hnq0oC8CiW95OtqZaqCGbawqsAw=/1412x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TZ54ASIBWVC4PCURFCPRS7LSSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHnq0oC8CiW95OtqZaqCGbawqsAw%3D%2F1412x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTZ54ASIBWVC4PCURFCPRS7LSSE.jpg&h=5b544e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多個康文署體育場地昨重開，維園球柱貼有安心出行二維碼貼。"},{"pid":"b490a848d710c5a805298384d1b7c5faf3a7abe5","tid":2415293,"uid":312363,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"攬住碌柱做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39740fcebc28a99e5bb9a816ab7675cb1b712a5a","tid":2415293,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"蘋果依家冇其他新聞報咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6a2534ec0c29c67371bbbfae852d4aea4ddcca","tid":2415293,"uid":48582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"點解睇到個topic就知係蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649f31326312e0ee178c3c009b600239a8f4f9d6","tid":2415293,"uid":378793,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b490a848d710c5a805298384d1b7c5faf3a7abe5","tid":2415293,"uid":312363,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"攬住碌柱做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"港男不嬲都弱智仔咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c61a6be39308a1f1f50451393ef084c91da13d","tid":2415293,"uid":237459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"毒果又維穩"},{"pid":"253b2ca898f3f36c74efc17e6a8310997c9c4908","tid":2415293,"uid":37112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"靜靜雞得唔得，點解一定要報出嚟？"},{"pid":"f16cda8e5ac8d4dfac6c004ebee130cc5aff482e","tid":2415293,"uid":46086,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b490a848d710c5a805298384d1b7c5faf3a7abe5","tid":2415293,"uid":312363,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"攬住碌柱做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm